title:{"type":"field","size":[492,17],"pos":[10,22],"locked":1,"font":"menu","show":"invert","border":1,"align":"center","value":"Paths: Wiggling"}
button3:{"type":"button","size":[60,20],"pos":[78,312],"script":"background.1","text":"Index","style":"rect"}
field1:{"type":"field","size":[209,106],"pos":[293,48],"locked":1,"border":0,"value":"We can add random offsets to each point in a path in order to give the text a wiggly, distorted appearance for visual effect.\n\nIt's possible to conform each line of the path against the same list of random deltas, but this produces a slightly different effect from the more expensive approach of producing new random deltas for each line segment. Experiment!"}
ex1:{"type":"field","size":[276,254],"pos":[10,48],"border":1,"scrollbar":1,"style":"code","value":"p:hershey.textpath[\n hf_futura\n \"Wiggliness?\"\n]\nc.clear[]\nc.brush:1\n\nw1:p+list 2 window random[3 50]-1\n\nw2:each x in p\n x+2 window random[3 2*count x]-1\nend\n\n\nc.pattern:colors.red\nc.line @ w1+list list 15,10\n\nc.pattern:colors.blue\nc.line @ w2+list list 15,45\n"}
